    <item>
      <title>利比亚将重启石油生产，结束严重危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/libya-to-restart-oil-production-ending-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚石油部长哈利法·阿布尔·萨迪克在接受彭博社采访时表示，利比亚将从周四开始恢复石油生产，此举有可能使利比亚在政治僵局之后每天数十万桶的石油重返全球市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/libya-to-restart-oil-production-ending-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦十年后重返美元债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/kazakhstan-returns-to-dollar-bond-market-after-decade-away</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年早些时候，一场引发资产扣押威胁的法律纠纷得到解决后，哈萨克斯坦近十年来首次重返美元债券市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/kazakhstan-returns-to-dollar-bond-market-after-decade-away</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:31:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳称债券持有人绝大多数支持债务重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/ghana-said-bondholders-overwhelmingly-support-debt-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳获得了国际债券持有人的“压倒性”参与和支持，重组了其 130 亿美元的海外债券，这是这个西非国家债务重组的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/ghana-said-bondholders-overwhelmingly-support-debt-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:30:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 内部人士股票销售额已超过 18 亿美元，未来还将有更多销售额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nvidia-insider-share-sales-top-1-8-billion-and-more-are-coming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年迄今为止，Nvidia Corp. 的内部人士已经套现了价值超过 18 亿美元的股票 — — 而且未来还会有更多的抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nvidia-insider-share-sales-top-1-8-billion-and-more-are-coming</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前花旗亚洲交易员在不公平解雇案中胜诉并达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/ex-citi-asia-desk-trader-settles-case-after-unfair-dismissal-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团与一名前交易员达成了就业诉讼和解，此前法官裁定，该交易员被花旗集团不公平解雇，原因是该交易员被当作该行十年来在为亚洲客户执行股票交易时违反监管规定的替罪羊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/ex-citi-asia-desk-trader-settles-case-after-unfair-dismissal-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:25:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝利宣布加快降息步伐，英镑或创 2022 年以来最大单日跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pound-hits-two-week-low-as-bailey-opens-door-to-more-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国央行行长安德鲁贝利暗示可能采取更积极的方式降低利率后，英镑有望出现一年多来最大幅度的下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pound-hits-two-week-low-as-bailey-opens-door-to-more-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 05:57:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美国期货下跌，中东风险上升，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股指期货下跌，因中东冲突升级的风险抑制了风险偏好，而经济数据可能会为美联储的政策走向提供更多指引。原油延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东供应风险主导油价连续第三天上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价连续第三天上涨，因为交易商评估了中东的供应风险，预计以色列将在本周早些时候对伊朗发动导弹袭击后对伊朗进行报复性打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
